That is not an indication of aggro decay, all it means is that someone else has more time to gain a larger amount of hate if you don't sit down immediately. That's very easy to test too. Have a cleric pull aggro by CHing, then have someone taunt off of the cleric without any attacking or doing anything else to increase aggro. Wait several minutes and then have the cleric sit down.</font></p>
	
